34
00:02:12.230 --> 00:02:15.290
What should I do, Tan Baba?

35
00:02:15.290 --> 00:02:18.060
Adviser, don't worry too much.

36
00:02:18.060 --> 00:02:22.270
This shameful husband must ultimately see his wife's younger brother, right?

37
00:02:25.300 --> 00:02:28.060
Qingchen still hasn't come out.

38
00:02:29.880 --> 00:02:33.800
The door to Sir's room is locked tightly. Nothing could have happened, right?

39
00:02:41.470 --> 00:02:44.430
Is there nothing that Sir Tang wants to say?

40
00:02:45.520 --> 00:02:47.500
What is it that you want to ask?

41
00:02:47.500 --> 00:02:51.050
There are many questions. Please answer them truthfully.

42
00:02:51.050 --> 00:02:53.200
I won't keep anything from you.

43
00:02:53.930 --> 00:02:58.070
Sir Tang, my older sister came to the government office only in order to gather source material.

44
00:02:58.070 --> 00:03:01.080
She never thought of standing out among everyone as an official.

45
00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:04.070
In these three months, she has entered prison and suffered injuries.

46
00:03:04.070 --> 00:03:07.490
And now, she has even been slandered as a murderer.

47
00:03:07.490 --> 00:03:11.840
Sir, ask yourself, do you have the ability to protect her?

48
00:03:13.010 --> 00:03:18.630
Qingchen, I am genuine and sincere in my feelings for your sister.

49
00:03:18.630 --> 00:03:22.840
Allowing her to be trapped in the middle of a quarrel of course isn't my real intention.

50
00:03:23.910 --> 00:03:25.930
I understand you.

51
00:03:25.930 --> 00:03:31.840
I can guarantee that from now on, I won't allow her to feel the least bit wronged.

52
00:03:31.840 --> 00:03:34.650
What will you use to guarantee this?

53
00:03:35.630 --> 00:03:40.310
With all due to respect, you pretended to be a corrupt officer and tricked Sun Yuanwai and the others.

54
00:03:40.310 --> 00:03:42.470
You used Sun Bufan to create a big issue,

55
00:03:42.470 --> 00:03:45.990
and caused an internal conflict between the upper class in Tongling.

56
00:03:45.990 --> 00:03:50.490
All of these were just so that you can investigate the gold mine case.

57
00:03:50.490 --> 00:03:54.820
Sir, you are a complicated man.

58
00:03:54.820 --> 00:03:58.090
If only she were as intelligent as you.

59
00:03:59.390 --> 00:04:02.000
Although I do not have any blood relation with my sister,

60
00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:05.260
but after my mother died so the two of us have relied on one another to survive.

61
00:04:05.260 --> 00:04:08.730
So, Sir, you should understand how much I value my sister.

62
00:04:08.730 --> 00:04:12.860
I comprehend what you mean and understand you.

63
00:04:12.860 --> 00:04:18.260
But I also value your sister very much.

64
00:04:18.260 --> 00:04:21.470
Sir, there is no need for you to force someone to do something.

65
00:04:21.470 --> 00:04:24.770
There are numerous women in the world. My sister really isn't a good match for you.

66
00:04:24.770 --> 00:04:29.400
Moreover, my sister must marry a person of a similar class as Tang Tianyuan.

67
00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:32.360
In all likelihood, you have also heard about him to some extent.

68
00:04:32.360 --> 00:04:35.750
Tang Tianyuan is the prototype for all of the characters in my sister's books.

69
00:04:35.750 --> 00:04:38.790
From this, my sister's infatuation with him can clearly be seen.



71
00:04:57.600 --> 00:05:00.060
I am Tang Tianyuan.

72
00:05:06.280 --> 00:05:09.340
I was ordered to handle the case here by the imperial decree.

73
00:05:09.340 --> 00:05:14.290
I not deliberately hiding the truth but I don't want to endanger her.

74
00:05:14.290 --> 00:05:17.190
But how long can you hide this from her?

75
00:05:17.190 --> 00:05:22.450
My sister worships you, but you are playing with her like this.

76
00:05:22.450 --> 00:05:26.960
So this time, I plan to spare no effort in asking for her forgiveness.

77
00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:29.900
So I can be worthy of her sincere feelings for me.

78
00:05:31.250 --> 00:05:34.840
I will inform her about all of this.

79
00:05:36.860 --> 00:05:38.690
Please don't.

80
00:05:40.530 --> 00:05:44.290
Sir Tang, for the time being, please do not inform my sister.

81
00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:46.630
Why?

82
00:05:46.630 --> 00:05:51.730
A lot of people are involved in the gold case.  Sister is already in danger for what little she knows.

83
00:05:51.730 --> 00:05:54.170
If she knew the truth now,

84
00:05:54.170 --> 00:05:56.780
I'm scared it would cause her more danger.

85
00:05:56.780 --> 00:06:01.860
Not to even mention, my sister is a straightforward person, she doesn't like being lied to.

86
00:06:01.860 --> 00:06:04.880
Let's discuss this matter later on.

87
00:06:15.790 --> 00:06:18.580
<i>[Meet me at my place.]</i>

88
00:06:34.160 --> 00:06:37.080
<i>[Shenghong Pavilion]</i>

89
00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:51.100
You're awake.

90
00:06:51.910 --> 00:06:54.070
You caught a cold.

91
00:06:54.070 --> 00:06:57.960
Here, drink this medicine.

92
00:06:58.790 --> 00:07:01.120
I don't need you to watch over me.

93
00:07:06.110 --> 00:07:08.610
You can be unwilling to see me,

94
00:07:08.610 --> 00:07:12.600
but you must take your medicine punctually.

95
00:07:12.600 --> 00:07:17.180
The medicine in this box is enough for you to use for a year.

96
00:07:17.180 --> 00:07:19.720
The prescription is also inside.

97
00:07:19.720 --> 00:07:22.600
There is another matter which I must tell you about.

98
00:07:22.600 --> 00:07:25.000
You had never been poisoned

99
00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:29.490
and had never been subjected to my shackles because of poisoning.

100
00:07:29.490 --> 00:07:32.240
It's only that from when you were small, your body has been weak.

101
00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:35.860
You had to take medicine every day.

102
00:07:35.860 --> 00:07:40.090
For not telling you the truth, I am sorry.

103
00:07:40.090 --> 00:07:43.340
What is it that you want me to do for you this time?

104
00:07:44.070 --> 00:07:47.470
This medicine has no color and no flavor.

105
00:07:47.470 --> 00:07:50.610
As long as it is sprinkled on the furniture of the bedroom,

106
00:07:50.610 --> 00:07:55.980
the person who gets poisoned will have their entire body fester and die in three days.

107
00:07:55.980 --> 00:07:59.400
This is indeed something that even the gods will not be aware of and ghosts will not be conscious of.

108
00:08:00.050 --> 00:08:03.920
You are... ready to let me go?

109
00:08:04.610 --> 00:08:08.080
After this business is taken care of, no one will know of your past,

110
00:08:08.080 --> 00:08:10.770
and no one will investigate your past.

111
00:08:10.770 --> 00:08:15.140
You and I will break all ties

112
00:08:15.140 --> 00:08:17.860
