113
00:08:28.460 --> 00:08:29.470
It really looks good.

114
00:08:29.470 --> 00:08:32.290
Sister, do you really like Sir Tang?

115
00:08:37.430 --> 00:08:39.100
But didn't you say before

116
00:08:39.100 --> 00:08:42.610
that you must marry a person that is as upright as Tang Tianyuan?

117
00:08:43.520 --> 00:08:45.860
If Tang Tianyuan appeared in front of you right now,

118
00:08:45.860 --> 00:08:49.050
would you still choose Tang Feilong, Sir Tang?

119
00:08:51.260 --> 00:08:54.340
Look. The moon tonight is very round.

120
00:08:54.340 --> 00:08:56.450
Sis!

121
00:09:00.730 --> 00:09:03.720
I have heard a lot about Tang Tianyuan.

122
00:09:03.720 --> 00:09:05.610
He's...

123
00:09:05.610 --> 00:09:08.850
an honorable and righteous man.

124
00:09:08.850 --> 00:09:11.890
LIke other girls, I chased after him.

125
00:09:11.890 --> 00:09:14.130
Who wouldn't like someone like that?

126
00:09:14.130 --> 00:09:18.230
Also, he's done a great favor for me.

127
00:09:18.230 --> 00:09:22.240
But being grateful is one thing. Love and gratefulness are different, right?

128
00:09:22.240 --> 00:09:23.660
Yes.

129
00:09:23.660 --> 00:09:27.210
Therefore, I thought about it.

130
00:09:27.210 --> 00:09:29.610
He is still my aspiration.

131
00:09:30.430 --> 00:09:34.800
LIke him, I want to be someone who is righteous that brings justice.

132
00:09:36.390 --> 00:09:38.680
He's like the moon.

133
00:09:38.680 --> 00:09:42.190
Faraway and shining brightly,

134
00:09:43.970 --> 00:09:47.060
No matter where I go, when I look up,

135
00:09:47.060 --> 00:09:51.150
