137
00:09:56.340 --> 00:09:59.650
What about Tang Feilong?

138
00:10:01.740 --> 00:10:05.590
He is like a fire in the winter cold.

139
00:10:05.590 --> 00:10:09.850
You can't hold yourself back. You just want to be a little closer,

140
00:10:09.850 --> 00:10:11.850
