161
00:11:27.470 --> 00:11:30.670
- Sister Lingyin, come light the fireworks! Come quickly. 
 - Okay

162
00:11:30.670 --> 00:11:33.590
Come on. Don't worry.

163
00:12:27.590 --> 00:12:30.730
<i>Sir Tang, please don't tell older sister yet.</i>

164
00:12:30.730 --> 00:12:32.320
<i>There's too much involved in the gold case.</i>

165
00:12:32.320 --> 00:12:34.970
<i>She only knows a little bit and is already in danger.</i>

166
00:12:34.970 --> 00:12:38.820
<i>If she knows the truth, I'm afraid it'll further endanger her.</i>

167
00:12:38.820 --> 00:12:41.330
<i>Besides, Sister Lingyin is a straightforward person.</i>

168
00:12:41.330 --> 00:12:42.810
<i>She can't accept being lied to.</i>

169
00:12:42.810 --> 00:12:46.050
<i>Let's put it aside for now.</i>

170
00:12:49.750 --> 00:12:51.360
Sir,

171
00:12:51.360 --> 00:12:53.120
what are you thinking about?

172
00:12:53.120 --> 00:12:55.160
Nothing.

173
00:12:55.160 --> 00:12:57.710
Thinking of Adviser Tan, right?

174
00:12:58.630 --> 00:13:02.610
When my wife and I first got together, I thought about her every day, too.

175
00:13:02.610 --> 00:13:04.840
I said it was nothing.

176
00:13:05.270 --> 00:13:07.230
Why are you being shy with me?

177
00:13:07.230 --> 00:13:10.500
It's not like I've never liked someone before.

178
00:13:13.330 --> 00:13:15.700
Sir, take a look.

179
00:13:15.700 --> 00:13:18.890
This is the portrait of the refugee that Adviser Tan drew.

180
00:13:18.890 --> 00:13:22.190
She said the refugee she met that day, is this man.

181
00:13:22.190 --> 00:13:26.130
But I really don't know how I should describe the essence of this portrait to our men.

182
00:13:26.130 --> 00:13:30.140
They all said this portrait looks a lot like me when I was younger.

183
00:13:31.070 --> 00:13:32.740
Indeed, it does.

184
00:13:32.740 --> 00:13:34.200
What?

185
00:13:35.610 --> 00:13:38.690
Let's wait till tomorrow when she comes to the county office and have her draw another one.

186
00:13:38.690 --> 00:13:40.940
Yes, Sir. I'll excuse myself.

187
00:13:40.940 --> 00:13:44.230
- Oh, right.
 - Sir, anything else you need?

188
00:13:44.930 --> 00:13:47.230
I have a question for you.

189
00:13:47.890 --> 00:13:49.770
I have a friend.

190
00:13:49.770 --> 00:13:52.800
- Friend? 
 - Right, friend of mine.

191
00:13:52.800 --> 00:13:57.800
Because of some personal reasons, he had lied to his wife.

192
00:13:57.800 --> 00:13:58.770
Lied to her?

193
00:13:58.770 --> 00:14:01.650
I want to ask, in this case,

194
00:14:01.650 --> 00:14:04.240
will your wife forgive you?

195
00:14:05.860 --> 00:14:09.600
It depends on how serious it is.

196
00:14:09.600 --> 00:14:12.570
Is it keeping a mistress?

197
00:14:12.570 --> 00:14:15.240
Or having a stash of money?

198
00:14:15.240 --> 00:14:16.390
Something more serious.

199
00:14:16.390 --> 00:14:17.940
More serious?

200
00:14:17.940 --> 00:14:18.930
Yes.

201
00:14:18.930 --> 00:14:22.830
As for my wife, it depends on her mental

202
00:14:22.830 --> 00:14:26.110
and physical involvement.

203
00:14:27.030 --> 00:14:29.840
Mentally,

204
00:14:29.840 --> 00:14:31.700
it's a white lie.

205
00:14:31.700 --> 00:14:33.130
A white lie.

206
00:14:33.130 --> 00:14:35.260
As for physical,

207
00:14:37.780 --> 00:14:40.130
no one is hurt yet.

208
00:14:40.130 --> 00:14:43.250
No one's hurt. My wife...

209
00:14:43.250 --> 00:14:46.280
would never let me off no matter what.

210
00:14:48.180 --> 00:14:50.190
So, all I can do is

211
00:14:50.190 --> 00:14:53.940
avoid getting her angry so I can live a long life.

212
00:15:00.060 --> 00:15:01.870
All right,

213
00:15:01.870 --> 00:15:04.080
you may leave.

214
00:15:04.080 --> 00:15:06.500
I'm going to head out later.

215
00:15:06.500 --> 00:15:08.050
Head out?

216
00:15:09.970 --> 00:15:13.280
Adviser Tan is not at the bookstore.

217
00:15:13.280 --> 00:15:15.340
Who told you I'm going to meet Adviser Tan?

218
00:15:15.340 --> 00:15:16.670
Not meet with Adviser Tan?

219
00:15:16.670 --> 00:15:20.860
She's not playing "The Little Fairy" tonight, is she?

220
00:15:43.030 --> 00:15:44.950
I can do it!

221
00:15:58.270 --> 00:16:01.530
It's pretty good!

222
00:16:01.530 --> 00:16:03.730
My Lady is beautiful.

223
00:16:33.530 --> 00:16:36.840
Where did she learn this from?

224
00:16:36.840 --> 00:16:39.440
Something you don't know, eh? Recently,

225
00:16:39.440 --> 00:16:43.370
she's been to Miaosheng House often to learn dancing from Miss Ruyi.

226
00:16:43.370 --> 00:16:46.370
A few days back, Miss Ruyi requested a few days off.

227
00:16:46.370 --> 00:16:49.700
Lingyin came to give it a try.

228
00:16:49.700 --> 00:16:52.320
Don't you have other dancers?

229
00:16:53.680 --> 00:16:56.370
Her dream as a child was to learn to dance.

230
00:16:56.370 --> 00:16:58.660
You don't know about this?

231
00:17:08.830 --> 00:17:11.400
Since Miaosheng House will close down soon,

232
00:17:11.400 --> 00:17:14.040
I don't think it's necessary for you to linger here in Tongling.

233
00:17:14.040 --> 00:17:18.960
In my opinion, you should go back to Jingnan

234
00:17:18.960 --> 00:17:21.530
and continue to be a rich playboy.

235
00:17:21.530 --> 00:17:23.900
Tang Feilong,

236
00:17:23.900 --> 00:17:26.580
do you think I'll admit defeat?

237
00:17:27.790 --> 00:17:30.700
I know she likes you now.

238
00:17:30.700 --> 00:17:33.900
But her liking you has no conflict with me liking her?

239
00:17:33.900 --> 00:17:37.760
As long as she hasn't married you, I still have a chance.

240
00:17:39.030 --> 00:17:44.430
Who knows? Maybe on a lucky day something bad may happen to you.

241
00:18:11.070 --> 00:18:12.460
Great!

242
00:18:14.960 --> 00:18:18.630
So pretty!

243
00:18:18.630 --> 00:18:21.880
<i>Be careful</i>

