00:18:23.230 --> 00:18:26.750
<i>Wow! This is so wonderful!</i>

245
00:18:28.220 --> 00:18:30.900
<i>They are a perfect couple!</i>

246
00:18:38.180 --> 00:18:41.170
<i>Sir Tang!</i>

247
00:18:42.750 --> 00:18:44.200
<i>Who would have thought?</i>

248
00:18:44.200 --> 00:18:48.410
♫ <i> The swaying branches of the weeping willow,
a home with a bridge over a flowing creek </i> ♫

249
00:18:48.410 --> 00:18:49.690
What's so nice about this?

250
00:18:49.690 --> 00:18:50.650
Stop talking!

251
00:18:50.650 --> 00:18:52.880
♫ <i> I hear a pipa’s tune transmitted from afar </i>♫

252
00:18:52.880 --> 00:18:54.980
What's good about any of this!

253
00:18:54.980 --> 00:18:57.260
Why did you come?

254
00:18:57.260 --> 00:19:00.180
Had enough fun?

255
00:19:00.180 --> 00:19:04.030
Let's go home.

256
00:19:04.770 --> 00:19:09.200
♫ <i> Your smile is brighter than the moon 
and puts flowers to shame </i> ♫

257
00:19:09.820 --> 00:19:13.930
I saw how great Miss Zhou's dance was...

258
00:19:13.930 --> 00:19:16.060
I wanted to give you a surprise

259
00:19:16.630 --> 00:19:20.600
You looked great dancing but in the future, can you stop dancing?

260
00:19:21.320 --> 00:19:22.920
Jealous?

261
00:19:22.920 --> 00:19:25.690
Are you afraid of everyone in Tongling falling in love with me?

262
00:19:25.690 --> 00:19:28.640
Then it's not just Zhu Dacong chasing me anymore.

263
00:19:29.410 --> 00:19:31.690
I don't care how many Zhu Dacong's there are.

264
00:19:31.690 --> 00:19:33.720
I just think it's too dangerous.

265
00:19:34.620 --> 00:19:37.090
You're jealous and you won't admit it.

266
00:19:37.090 --> 00:19:40.990
What's so hard about admitting it?

267
00:19:40.990 --> 00:19:45.040
♫ <i>I’m destined to protect you in this lifetime </i> ♫

268
00:19:50.190 --> 00:19:51.570
Is it pretty?

269
00:19:53.340 --> 00:19:55.450
This red doesn't suit you.

270
00:20:01.550 --> 00:20:03.530
This one's pretty cute.

271
00:20:06.290 --> 00:20:08.030
Put it on for me.

272
00:20:09.590 --> 00:20:14.910
♫  <i>Filling the world with my concerns, I look for her everywhere </i> ♫

273
00:20:14.910 --> 00:20:20.020
♫ <i> A life that was supposed to be lived freely is now wasted </i>  ♫

274
00:20:20.020 --> 00:20:25.110
♫ <i> Walking slowing underneath a paper umbrella, you look like 
a piece of art in this misty rain </i> ♫

275
00:20:25.110 --> 00:20:26.970
Pretty?

276
00:20:26.970 --> 00:20:28.950
Pretty.

277
00:20:28.950 --> 00:20:32.920
- Spend your money! 
 - This one costs 3 taels.

278
00:20:32.920 --> 00:20:34.440
Thank you.

279
00:20:35.330 --> 00:20:36.690
Let's go!

280
00:20:42.150 --> 00:20:43.950
<i>[Be of good virtue and diligent]</i>

281
00:20:49.330 --> 00:20:51.120
I can't anymore!

282
00:20:53.750 --> 00:20:56.280
Then rest for a bit. Then go for another few minutes.

283
00:20:56.280 --> 00:20:58.130
No more, I'm so tired.

284
00:20:58.130 --> 00:21:00.270
Compared to useless hobbies like dancing,

285
00:21:00.270 --> 00:21:03.010
learning martial arts is more practical. It's self-defense.

286
00:21:03.010 --> 00:21:05.470
But aren't you here?

287
00:21:07.790 --> 00:21:09.420
Lingyin,

288
00:21:09.420 --> 00:21:12.770
I'm not your shadow. I can't follow you around all day.

289
00:21:12.770 --> 00:21:15.960
We haven't found the refugee that attacked you.

290
00:21:15.960 --> 00:21:18.880
If you encounter him again, what are you going to do?

291
00:21:18.880 --> 00:21:22.050
That's impossible. Why would I be so unlucky?

292
00:21:23.020 --> 00:21:25.340
Where's Zheng Shaofeng? Let him teach you.

293
00:21:25.340 --> 00:21:28.300
I haven't seen him in days.

294
00:21:29.350 --> 00:21:33.880
He's probably on a date with his beauty on Mount Tianmu.

295
00:21:33.880 --> 00:21:35.960
Look at Constable Zheng!

296
00:21:35.960 --> 00:21:38.690
Even a rough guy like him understands romance.

297
00:21:38.690 --> 00:21:42.150
He embroiders lotus flowers and goes chicken hunting at Mount Tianmu.

298
00:21:42.150 --> 00:21:46.400
What about you? Keeping me here to do squats daily.

299
00:21:48.260 --> 00:21:50.320
You want to hunt for chickens, too?

300
00:21:51.210 --> 00:21:53.990
How about we hunt something else today?

301
00:21:53.990 --> 00:21:55.020
Really?

302
00:21:55.020 --> 00:21:56.380
Really.

303
00:22:00.830 --> 00:22:03.290
Sir, wear this for me.

304
00:22:03.290 --> 00:22:05.160
Just wear it.

305
00:22:05.160 --> 00:22:06.880
No, it's too dumb.

306
00:22:06.880 --> 00:22:08.540
Then I'm leaving.

307
00:22:10.080 --> 00:22:11.600
I didn't bring any fireworks.

308
00:22:11.600 --> 00:22:15.010
If you don't want to be taken by wolves, don't run around.

309
00:22:15.010 --> 00:22:17.670
Constable Zheng is so nice to Miss Ruyi.

310
00:22:17.670 --> 00:22:21.190
If he holds her in his palms, he's afraid she'll fall. If he keeps her in his mouth, he's afraid she'll melt.

311
00:22:21.190 --> 00:22:24.990
And you? You treat me like your servant.

312
00:22:24.990 --> 00:22:27.120
I'm afraid you're too heavy to be held in my palms.

313
00:22:27.120 --> 00:22:30.050
How about you get on the horse?

314
00:22:36.500 --> 00:22:39.780
Deer! Look, Sir, there's a deer here.

315
00:22:39.780 --> 00:22:41.300
Give me the bow.

316
00:22:43.050 --> 00:22:45.460
Nevermind, we don't need to eat it.

317
00:22:45.460 --> 00:22:48.210
There's no need to slaughter a living creature.

318
00:22:48.210 --> 00:22:50.270
- It's fine to just look. 
 - Constable Zheng

319
00:22:50.270 --> 00:22:51.760
brought back a chicken.

320
00:22:51.760 --> 00:22:55.060
If I come back empty-handed, he'll look down on me.

321
00:22:55.060 --> 00:22:58.030
Immature. Why compare stuff like this?

322
00:22:58.030 --> 00:23:00.820
Shouldn't you guys compare the good traits of your lovers?

323
00:23:01.560 --> 00:23:04.480
He says there's a cliff cave near here. Let's take a look.

324
00:23:04.480 --> 00:23:06.890
What? Why don't you say something?

325
00:23:06.890 --> 00:23:09.290
Say something.

326
00:23:09.290 --> 00:23:12.380
Is it because I have too many good traits? You can't mention all of them?

327
00:23:12.380 --> 00:23:15.730
Anything. Just say one.

328
00:23:15.730 --> 00:23:18.090
Stop talking. I'm thinking.

329
00:23:28.300 --> 00:23:30.700
So this is the cave.

330
00:23:37.420 --> 00:23:39.950
There's dry wood and a fire... 
<i> (T/N: also an idiom that expresses passionate feelings between a couple)</i>

331
00:23:39.950 --> 00:23:44.420
Constable Zheng and Miss Ruyi were probably here on a date.

332
00:23:51.790 --> 00:23:54.370
He sure knows how to choose a place.

333
00:23:55.010 --> 00:23:56.880
What are you looking at?

334
00:23:58.750 --> 00:24:01.800
This is dry grass that was placed down for sleeping.

335
00:24:03.630 --> 00:24:05.910
And those marks on the wall

336
00:24:06.490 --> 00:24:08.790
were probably used to count days.

337
00:24:08.790 --> 00:24:11.380
If I guessed correctly,

338
00:24:11.380 --> 00:24:14.740
this place is the hideaway for refugees.

339
00:24:15.730 --> 00:24:20.430
Refugees? Haven't they all died?

340
00:24:21.180 --> 00:24:23.960
Then was the one you met on the street a ghost?

341
00:24:26.050 --> 00:24:27.210
That's right.

342
00:24:27.210 --> 00:24:30.190
He must've stayed here after successfully escaping from Sang Jie.

343
00:24:30.190 --> 00:24:33.090
If we find him, do we also find the evidence?

344
00:24:36.650 --> 00:24:39.440
This task... I'm relying on you.

345
00:24:40.820 --> 00:24:44.260
<i> [Miaosheng House]</i>

346
00:24:44.260 --> 00:24:45.610
Boss,

347
00:24:45.610 --> 00:24:48.540
we've been operating at a deficit for weeks.

348
00:24:48.540 --> 00:24:50.730
We didn't earn much these last few days either.

349
00:24:50.730 --> 00:24:54.750
How long are you going to hold out for until we close down?

350
00:24:56.590 --> 00:24:58.750
Until my fiancee changes her mind

351
00:24:58.750 --> 00:25:01.000
and agrees to go back to Jinan with me.

352
00:25:01.000 --> 00:25:03.850
I'll close this place then.

353
00:25:04.630 --> 00:25:09.140
It looks like our business has a chance of becoming a century-old brand.

354
00:25:09.490 --> 00:25:11.880
Don't jinx me!

355
00:25:13.230 --> 00:25:15.110
Let me tell you.

356
00:25:15.890 --> 00:25:17.740
I have a

357
00:25:18.690 --> 00:25:22.020
strong premonition.

358
00:25:26.300 --> 00:25:30.570
My fiancee and Tang Feilong

359
00:25:31.430 --> 00:25:34.050
are about to separate.

360
00:25:34.600 --> 00:25:37.040
<i>[Morality]</i>

361
00:25:39.940 --> 00:25:42.340
<i>[Tongling County Office]</i>

362
00:25:58.300 --> 00:26:01.030
<i>[Tongling County Office]</i>

363
00:26:08.430 --> 00:26:10.680
<i>[Jiang Muchun, special appearance]</i>

364
00:26:15.120 --> 00:26:16.710
I remember him

365
00:26:16.710 --> 00:26:19.680
having messy hair.

366
00:26:19.680 --> 00:26:23.410
His eyebrows were thick. His eyes were big.

367
00:26:23.410 --> 00:26:26.060
His nose was thin.

368
00:26:26.060 --> 00:26:28.540
His mouth was a little pouty.

369
00:26:30.640 --> 00:26:35.560
If you just look at his features, he looks like a regular young scholar.

370
00:26:35.560 --> 00:26:39.100
But with his layered and tattered clothes

371
00:26:39.100 --> 00:26:42.000
along with his fierce expression,

372
00:26:42.000 --> 00:26:43.370
he...

373
00:26:43.370 --> 00:26:47.580
has the temperament of a brave army general.

374
00:26:53.220 --> 00:26:56.030
A collapsed nose bridge means he's lethargic.

375
00:26:56.030 --> 00:26:59.490
Once he's middle-aged, he'll have kidney problems.

376
00:26:59.490 --> 00:27:02.650
Thin lips suggest he's cold-hearted.

377
00:27:02.650 --> 00:27:06.220
Someone who's easily offended and quick to start arguments.

378
00:27:07.170 --> 00:27:10.620
Tell me. What kind of guy

379
00:27:10.620 --> 00:27:15.350
is affectionate and has the ability to hold onto vast wealth?

380
00:27:15.350 --> 00:27:17.760
Let me know... I'll give it some thought.

381
00:27:17.760 --> 00:27:20.740
In the future when I look for a husband, I'll try to find someone with that kind of appearance.

382
00:27:24.320 --> 00:27:26.180
Are you mad?

383
00:27:26.180 --> 00:27:28.110
Why would I be mad?

384
00:27:28.110 --> 00:27:31.150
Why would I get mad over a refugee bandit?

385
00:27:31.150 --> 00:27:35.050
Then, why did you draw him like that? It's so ugly, like a pig head.

386
00:27:35.050 --> 00:27:37.090
It's true that he's ugly.

387
00:27:37.090 --> 00:27:40.420
According to you, thick eyebrows and big eyes,

388
00:27:40.420 --> 00:27:44.460
a flat nose and thin lips. Doesn't he look like this?

389
00:27:47.100 --> 00:27:51.940
Look at what you drew! Give it. I'll draw him myself.

390
00:27:55.310 --> 00:27:59.360
Just admit it if you're jealous. Men are just so—

391
00:27:59.360 --> 00:28:00.970
Sir!

392
00:28:02.440 --> 00:28:05.570
Sir, there's a lady outside

393
00:28:05.570 --> 00:28:09.230
saying her fiance ran away from his marriage. She's asking you to give her justice.

394
00:28:09.230 --> 00:28:11.530
Escaping from marriage?

395
00:28:11.530 --> 00:28:13.970
Isn't she the female version of Zhu Dacong?

396
00:28:13.970 --> 00:28:18.200
A man who can do such a thing is extremely irresponsible.

397
00:28:18.200 --> 00:28:21.510
You can't trust him with your life.

398
00:28:21.510 --> 00:28:25.320
I think we should convince her to give up.

399
00:28:25.320 --> 00:28:29.420
I think you should let me handle this. I'll take her to see Zhu Dacong.

400
00:28:29.420 --> 00:28:31.980
They can exchange their feelings.

401
00:28:31.980 --> 00:28:36.890
Who knows? They might get together and I would have promoted a marriage.

402
00:28:37.560 --> 00:28:40.040
Adviser, she's right outside.

403
00:28:40.040 --> 00:28:41.620
Okay, I'm going to go.

404
00:28:43.610 --> 00:28:45.200
Let's go.

405
00:28:55.110 --> 00:28:57.820
Heavenly Fairy. Heavenly Fairy!

406
00:28:58.740 --> 00:29:01.190
Only my wife can be the Heavenly Fairy.

407
00:29:02.060 --> 00:29:05.030
Pretty, she's very pretty. She's definitely not below Adviser Tan.

408
00:29:05.030 --> 00:29:07.170
Don't you want to go look?

409
00:29:08.460 --> 00:29:11.810
Pretty, very pretty, right? No, thanks.

410
00:29:13.910 --> 00:29:16.720
One look, you can tell she's the daughter of a wealthy family.

411
00:29:16.720 --> 00:29:18.410
Adviser Tan is short-tempered.

412
00:29:18.410 --> 00:29:22.120
Who is like a pearl and who is like a fish's eye can be clearly seen from a single glance.

413
00:29:29.180 --> 00:29:31.200
Only you can see it.

414
00:29:33.630 --> 00:29:37.390
These days... you've surely learned a lot of words.

415
00:29:37.390 --> 00:29:39.890
<i>[Hall of Justice and Integrity]</i>

416
00:29:39.890 --> 00:29:41.650
Adviser.

417
00:29:42.440 --> 00:29:44.790
It's you that struck the drum to voice a grievance?

418
00:29:44.790 --> 00:29:46.940
Yes, as you stated.

419
00:29:46.940 --> 00:29:49.110
Miss, may I ask what your name is?

420
00:29:49.110 --> 00:29:50.860
My name is Jiang Muchun.

421
00:29:50.860 --> 00:29:52.940
Is your husband blind?

422
00:29:52.940 --> 00:29:56.260
You are so beautiful and he still wants to run away from your marriage.

423
00:29:56.260 --> 00:29:58.530
- It's a long story. 
 - Relax and tell me.

424
00:29:58.530 --> 00:30:02.300
As long as he is in Tongling County, I will surely catch him.

425
00:30:02.300 --> 00:30:04.550
What is his name?

426
00:30:04.550 --> 00:30:07.940
He is the grand secretary of the emperor, Tang Tianyuan.

427
00:30:08.700 --> 00:30:11.220
Tang... Tang Tianyuan?

428
00:30:11.920 --> 00:30:14.430
Tang Tianyuan has a fiancee?

429
00:30:16.830 --> 00:30:20.570
Isn't Tang Tianyuan at the capital? Why did you come to Tongling?

430
00:30:20.570 --> 00:30:22.880
He's here in Tongling.

431
00:30:22.880 --> 00:30:25.300
Just inside this county office.

432
00:30:28.650 --> 00:30:30.560
Is it the wrong person?

433
00:30:30.560 --> 00:30:34.730
- We only have an eighth class magistrate, Tang Feilong. There's no Tang Tianyuan. 
 - No.

434
00:30:34.730 --> 00:30:39.250
Don't you know? Tang Feilong is Tang Tianyuan's alias.

435
00:30:39.250 --> 00:30:41.490
They're the same person.

436
00:30:42.130 --> 00:30:45.090
Xi Hulu, is My Lord there?

437
00:30:52.820 --> 00:30:57.080
<i>This... Isn't it the story from my book? </i>

438
00:31:11.280 --> 00:31:15.870
♫<i> Our shadows are cast as we walk into the double corridor </i>♫

439
00:31:15.870 --> 00:31:22.400
♫<i> You held the mirror and lightly touch up your rouge </i>♫

440
00:31:22.400 --> 00:31:25.470
♫<i> You held the mirror and lightly touch up your rouge </i>♫

441
00:31:27.000 --> 00:31:29.950
Miss Jiang, please.

442
00:31:29.950 --> 00:31:33.730
♫<i> We'll not forget each other </i>♫

443
00:31:33.730 --> 00:31:38.930
♫<i> And you're like the starry dream </i>♫

444
00:31:41.230 --> 00:31:44.050
Tang Feilong is Tang Tianyuan?

445
00:31:44.050 --> 00:31:46.520
He has a fiancee?

446
00:31:47.740 --> 00:31:49.500
I don't know.

447
00:31:54.570 --> 00:31:56.260
Adviser!

448
00:31:58.070 --> 00:31:59.420
Sir Tang is coming.

449
00:31:59.420 --> 00:32:03.540
- Where's Adviser Tan? 
 - She left without saying anything.

450
00:32:03.540 --> 00:32:07.450
Sir Tang, long time no see.

451
00:32:07.980 --> 00:32:09.880
How come you came?

452
00:32:10.860 --> 00:32:12.900
Auntie said she misses you. 
<i>(T/N: Auntie is referring to Tianyuan's mom.)</i>

453
00:32:12.900 --> 00:32:15.900
She wanted me to come and visit and see how you're doing.

454
00:32:15.900 --> 00:32:17.970
Where are you staying?

455
00:32:26.030 --> 00:32:27.980
You arrange this.

456
00:32:31.300 --> 00:32:33.490
Thank you, Sir.

457
00:32:35.090 --> 00:32:39.230
<i> [Be of good virtue and diligent] </i>

458
00:32:43.300 --> 00:32:45.190
Miss Jiang.

459
00:32:53.780 --> 00:32:57.100
♫<i>  There's no wind, there's no love. There's no sense of loss </i>♫

460
00:32:57.100 --> 00:33:01.700
♫<i> There's no you, there's no pain. Can't hear
 the uneasiness in my heart </i>♫

461
00:33:02.910 --> 00:33:07.650
Tan Lingyin!

462
00:33:07.650 --> 00:33:11.320
♫<i> There's no lamp, there's no sound. Don't feel out of place </i>♫

463
00:33:11.320 --> 00:33:14.150
♫<i> There's no one reciting old monologues in my mind </i>♫

464
00:33:14.150 --> 00:33:16.250
Sir, please head home.

465
00:33:16.250 --> 00:33:18.450
My sister doesn't want to see you.

466
00:33:19.130 --> 00:33:22.420
Sir, don't make it hard for me.

467
00:33:22.420 --> 00:33:26.810
My sister doesn't know how to face you right now. It's better to not to see each other right now.

468
00:33:26.810 --> 00:33:28.700
I'll explain what happened to her.

469
00:33:28.700 --> 00:33:30.840
She'll understand.

470
00:33:31.510 --> 00:33:34.140
I really didn't mean to deceive her.

471
00:33:34.140 --> 00:33:37.710
I understand. But right now,

472
00:33:37.710 --> 00:33:41.760
if you really want her to forgive you, give her some time.

473
00:33:41.760 --> 00:33:48.920
♫<i> I lowered my expectations of happiness </i>♫

474
00:33:48.920 --> 00:33:53.470
♫<i> Do I still love? Is love still there? </i>♫

475
00:33:53.470 --> 00:34:00.490
♫<i> The answers keep changing, illusions from the tears kept me </i>♫

476
00:34:00.490 --> 00:34:07.660
♫<i> from letting go. I wrestled with these tangled thoughts </i>♫

477
00:34:07.660 --> 00:34:13.240
♫<i> Always end up with confused and wrong answers </i>♫

478
00:34:13.240 --> 00:34:17.770
♫<i> The verdict never comes </i>♫

479
00:34:18.300 --> 00:34:20.780
Assistant Zhou, you're finally back!

480
00:34:20.780 --> 00:34:23.770
Constable Zheng has been looking for your sister...

481
00:34:23.770 --> 00:34:27.310
and you. He looked for a long time, and just couldn't find you guys.

482
00:34:27.310 --> 00:34:30.060
He always says you guys disappear together.

483
00:34:30.060 --> 00:34:33.540
Convinced that both of you were kidnapped, he wanted to call the authorities. Thank goodness we stopped him.

484
00:34:33.540 --> 00:34:36.000
Go talk some sense into him.

485
00:34:42.040 --> 00:34:43.940
Zheng Shaofeng!

486
00:34:45.220 --> 00:34:48.860
Get up.

487
00:34:52.440 --> 00:34:56.240
- What? 
 - Is it necessary to go as far as to death for a woman?

488
00:34:56.240 --> 00:34:59.300
I-I'm thirsty. I'm drinking some water.

489
00:34:59.300 --> 00:35:01.480
What are you doing?

490
00:35:03.460 --> 00:35:07.130
Drink... If you want to drink, there's a bucket.

